title: How to Be Deadly [2014 - Newfoundland - Canada]
description:
How to Be Deadly (2014 - Canada)

Comedy
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt4022208/


Filmed at St. John's, Newfoundland, Newfoundland and Labrador, Canada

Donnie Dumphy is out to prove he's the deadliest boy on The Rock. The night before the big dirt-bike competition this working-class hero cashes his welfare cheque, tours the worst parts of town, eats fish n' chips, loses his old dear Brenda, has a mug-up with his Nan, near drowns and sleeps with his social worker - all before the boats set out at sunrise.
